OL,3,CGarden centre CCTV shows couple hiding
OL,4,Cstolen items in baby's pram
OL,6,FA garden centre says it has lost
OL,7,Faround #1m in stock in three years
OL,8,Fafter a spate of shoplifting incidents.
OL,10,FTates of Sussex runs four garden
OL,11,Fcentres and says the crime has become
OL,12,Ffar too frequent, which not only hits
OL,13,Fprofits, but threatens the welfare of
OL,14,Fstaff and customers too.
OL,16,FThe company has spent more than
OL,17,F#100,000 to boost security at its
OL,18,Fbranches. One couple was seen on CCTV
OL,19,Fat its Brighton concealing items in a
OL,20,Fbaby's pram.
