OL,6,FNew figures from Sussex Police shows
OL,7,Fthat shoplifting has risen 40%, which
OL,8,Fis well above the national average of
OL,9,F28%. It is the second highest rise
OL,10,Foutside London.
OL,12,FAn inquiry on Tuesday (5 November) by
OL,13,Fthe House of Lords reported that shop
OL,14,Ftheft has evolved from what it called
OL,15,F'individualised offending' to
OL,16,Frelentless large-scale organised
OL,17,Foperations accompanied by
OL,18,Funprecedented levels of violence.
