OL,6,FThe force said it is committed to
OL,7,Ftackling all types of acquisitive
OL,8,Fcrime and understand the traumatic
OL,9,Fimpact robbery and theft has. It also
OL,10,Fsaid it has dedicated officers working
OL,11,Fto identify offenders and prosecute
OL,12,Fthem.
OL,14,FThe force said another factor to take
OL,15,Finto account, for the apparent rise in
OL,16,Fshoplifting in the county, is partly
OL,17,Fdue to more people reporting it.
