OL,6,FChristopher Hoare, Head of Security,
OL,7,FTates of Sussex said: "It's a growing
OL,8,Fproblem for us. It's becoming more and
OL,9,Fmore prolific, with gangs now
OL,10,Ftargeting us.
OL,12,F"It's no longer just individual items
OL,13,Fthat people are coming in for everyday
OL,14,Fuse, but they're taking large volumes
OL,15,Fof stock.
OL,17,F"I think the biggest problem that
OL,18,Fpolice have is that they're under
OL,19,Fresourced and under manned."
