OL,6,FChris Neilson, Business Crime Lead for
OL,7,FSussex Police said: "Sussex Police
OL,8,Fabsolutely understands the financial
OL,9,Fand personal impact of shoplifting on
OL,10,Fbusiness owners, employees and the
OL,11,Fwider community.
OL,13,F"We use a range of powers at our
OL,14,Fdisposal, alongside charges, to reach
OL,15,Fa satisfactory conclusion for victims.
OL,16,FThis includes civil orders and
OL,17,Fcommunity resolutions aimed at
OL,18,Fmanaging offenders and bringing about
OL,19,Fbehavioural change.
