OL,6,F"Significant investment and engagement
OL,7,Fhas gone towards making reporting as
OL,8,Feasy as possible, which has naturally
OL,9,Fseen an increase in the number of
OL,10,Freports.
OL,12,F"We investigate whenever there are
OL,13,Freasonable lines of enquiry, such as
OL,14,FCCTV, vehicles or possible suspects.
OL,15,FWe prioritise cases if violence has
OL,16,Fbeen used, if a person has been
OL,17,Fdetained, if offending is prolific or
OL,18,Fif it is linked to other incidents."
